# Design System Enforcement Rules

## 1. Detect Which System

| Signal | System |
|---|---|
| `@salt-ds/`, `SaltProvider`, `--salt-*`, `.salt-` | **Salt DS** |
| `@mui/`, `ThemeProvider`, `--md-sys-*`, Material | **Material 3** |
| `@fluentui/`, `FluentProvider`, `--color*Brand*` | **Fluent 2** |

