## 4. Material 3 Rules

### Spacing: 8dp baseline grid (4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64dp)

### Shape Scale
```
Extra Small: 4dp   (text fields, menus)
Small:       8dp   (chips, snackbars)
Medium:      12dp  (cards, dialogs)
Large:       16dp  (navigation drawers)
Extra Large: 28dp  (FABs, search bars)
```

### Elevation = Tonal (NOT shadow) in light theme
```
Level 0: surface                    Level 3: surfaceContainerHigh
Level 1: surfaceContainerLow        Level 4: surfaceContainerHighest
Level 2: surfaceContainer           Level 5: shadow (modals only)
```

### State Layers (opacity overlay of content color)
- Hover: 8% | Focus: 10% | Press: 10% | Dragged: 16%

---

## 5. Fluent 2 Rules

### Component Sizes
```
Small:  24px height, 12px font
Medium: 32px height, 14px font (DEFAULT)
Large:  40px height, 14px font
```

### Corner Radius: 4px default. Cards 8px. Dialogs 8px.

### Elevation: Dual shadow (key + ambient), always use both together.

### Motion
- Entries: decelerate `cubic-bezier(0.1, 0.9, 0.2, 1)`
- Exits: accelerate `cubic-bezier(0.9, 0.1, 1, 0.2)`

---

## 6. Common Violations

| Violation | Fix |
|---|---|
| Raw hex `#1B7F9E` | `var(--salt-palette-accent)` |
| `padding: 15px` | `var(--salt-spacing-200)` |
| `border-radius: 7px` | `var(--salt-curve-100)` |
| Button `appearance="filled"` | Salt: `appearance="solid"` |
| Missing validation states | Wrap in `<FormField validationStatus="error">` |
| No focus ring | `:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--token) }` |
| Shadow in M3 light theme | Use tonal surface, not drop shadow |
| Hardcoded dark colors | Use semantic tokens that auto-switch |
